The '''2011 [[CrossFit Games]]''' were held on July 29–31, 2011, at the [[Home Depot Center]] in [[Carson, California]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://games.crossfit.com/history-of-the-games |title=History &#124; CrossFit Games |publisher=Games.crossfit.com |date= |accessdate=August 7, 2017}}</ref> The men's competition was won by [[Rich Froning]], and the women's by [[Annie Thorisdottir]]. 2011 marked the first year of the "CrossFit Games Open" as the first stage of the qualification process for the CrossFit Games; online submissions of workout results were invited from competitors worldwide.
